    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but it feels like a lot of unnecessary medicine if the infection is already gone. i've read that taking antibiotics when you don't strictly need them can mess up your gut microbiome and cause other issues. if the symptoms are 100% gone, isn't it actually healthier to just stop before we cause more side effects?",
