      "content": "The \"rule\" is because the infection is hiding, not because you can see it! You stop when the *bacteria* are gone, not when the *redness* is gone. If you stop now, you're just giving the microscopic villains a chance to throw a party and come back stronger. Trust the science, not your fleeting feeling of wellness. Finish the full course, and you'll be a walking testament to proper medical adherence.",
